data.description: 3BD/3BA home located in a serene country setting. From the moment you walk onto the welcoming front porch, you will feel right at home. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, cream cabinetry, beautiful countertops, and direct access to the backyard. Downstairs bathrooms include double sinks and mirrors making it easy to share . There is also a bonus room upstairs with a FULL bath and a walk-in access to the attic, perfect for storage. Open landscape allows for care free living and the back deck gives you room to enjoy the outdoors. Call for an appointment today!
